reviewText: The two Lamb of God DVDs and the Black Dahlia Murder DVD have set the bar high for band DVDs and this one from Evergreen Terrace falls well below

this is a got to have dvd, Evergreen Terrace is such a great band and they bring so much more to the hardcore scene with positive lyrics, melodic riffs and gut busting vocals. I cant say enough about this band, go out and buy their cd's and dvd
